ge. You've even already attended an agile training course. I am thrilled that you are part of this team and can't wait to see how you help take our Marketing team to the next level.\n\n202#Off to a great start...|Welcome to the team John! Your first week has been filled with new faces, names, meetings, a marketing offsite, and a cold. Thank you for all the listening you‚Äôve done because as much as we tried to give you a human start... we are excited to have you and bring some positive changes to the workflow! It‚Äôs been a busy week, but a good week with your support for not only us, but everyone. Happy to have you here!\n\n"
